 World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132160897,imgsize-78697.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Heatwave safety steps: Experts urge precautions to prevent heatstroke]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132160142.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A scorching heatwave is sweeping across the central and eastern United States, pushing temperatures up to 105°F right before the Fourth of July festivities. Health officials are stressing the importance of caution, particularly for vulnerable populations, as the risk of heatstroke is notably high. Staying hydrated, donning appropriate clothing, and being aware of the symptoms are essential for surviving the extreme heat, expected to linger through the weekend.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/extreme-heatwave-scorches-us-ahead-of-fourth-of-july-holiday-5-outdoor-safety-tips-you-should-know/articleshow/132160142.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/extreme-heatwave-scorches-us-ahead-of-fourth-of-july-holiday-5-outdoor-safety-tips-you-should-know/articleshow/132160142.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-03T17:10:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Lifestyle Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132160259,imgsize-212042.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[First underwater home for scientists installed 17 metres below the Florida Keys]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132159194.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/first-underwater-home-for-scientists-installed-17-metres-below-the-florida-keys-to-support-marine-research/articleshow/13